query:
INSERT INTO
                    scheduler_witness_jobs_fri (
                        l1_batch_number,
                        scheduler_partial_input_blob_url,
                        protocol_version,
                        status,
                        created_at,
                        updated_at,
                        protocol_version_patch
                    )
                VALUES
                    ($1, $2, $3, 'waiting_for_proofs', NOW(), NOW(), $4)
                ON CONFLICT (l1_batch_number) DO
                UPDATE
                SET
                    updated_at = NOW()
